title: Ep45 Gossip at the Corpse Cart
description:
This month's GACC brings you a violent robot, a not-great place to take a nap, some BAD Olive Garden, thoughts and prayers, mystery scat, a floating foot, and one very Aussie obit. Tune in for Gossip at the Corpse Cart!

For a full list of show sponsors, visit https://wineandcrimepodcast.com/sponsors/
